cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with data acquisition from a wireless sensor network, which involves signal processing, information theory, and networking. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a machine learning-based method for finding a suitable representation basis, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with the optimization of network transmissions, which can be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
